# Delegation Protocol

This project uses a delegation workflow between Claude Code and Cursor.

## Before You Start
1. Read `CURSOR_INBOX.md` for pending task assignments
2. Work on the highest-priority uncompleted task first
3. Follow the acceptance criteria listed in each task
4. When done, mark the task checkbox `[x]` and add a completion note under it

## After You Finish
- Commit your changes with a clear message referencing the task ID
- If a task has a "Report Back" section, leave your findings as a note in `CURSOR_INBOX.md`
- Move to the next uncompleted task, or wait for new assignments
